{"tid":1397483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角遊行上訴 獲批大角咀過馬路遊行","createTime":"2019-08-02T13:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T13:45:52.000Z","uid":10973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc79c716ead3318a63b619fa8724e33bb291c7b","tid":1397483,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"旺角遊行上訴 獲批大角咀過馬路遊行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/336CW8q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F336CW8q&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=00b47111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/336CW8q</a><br />\n<br />\n網民早前申請於明日（8月2日）在旺角遊行及集會，但是警方僅批准集會部份。申請人伍永德上訴，今日經2小時半聆訊後，與警方達成共識，將遊行路線大幅修改，變為由大角咀晏架街遊樂場，橫過一條櫻桃街馬路至櫻桃街公園為終點，完全不經旺角市中心。"},{"pid":"25442448a19116d4d479c100812caf876ec84708","tid":1397483,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390913</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有興趣請入Group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=0cd95b2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"71ed07ac61d482bc3184b708675da12776361213","tid":1397483,"uid":32655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:30:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8f0eb123abd52ee94ffb35c3fd5305c51021205","tid":1397483,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"聽日就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae0138f1a790fb2e12b3a43554374d3cda4456d","tid":1397483,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8f0eb123abd52ee94ffb35c3fd5305c51021205","tid":13